se.com/home/kultur/kunst/5127286/Ist-das-Kunst-Ist-das-Recht-Oder-beides Article by Almuth Spiegler in] [[Die Presse]] (Austrian newspaper), November 30, 2016</ref>\n* 2016,  section project statements of Parallel Vienna: exhibition ''Border Crossing'' with Pablo Chiereghin, Guido Kucsko, Esther Stocker and Hana Usui.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marcello-farabegoli.net/parallel-vienna-2016.html|title=Parallel Vienna 2016|website=www.marcello-farabegoli.net|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://parallelvienna.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/PARALLEL-VIENNA-2016-press-text-EN.pdf|title=Homepage of the art fair Parallel Vienna|publisher=|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eop.at/parallelvienna/|title=eop - emergence of projects  - PARALLEL VIENNA|website=www.eop.at|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref>\n* 2016, Italian embassy - Palais Metternich Vienna: exhibition ''Geometries'' by Esther Stocker inaugurated by Giorgio Marrapodi, Italian ambassador, Meinhard Rauchensteiner, adviser for science, art and culture of the President of Austria, Christoph Thun-Hohenstein, general director of [[Museum of Applied Arts, Vienna|MAK\u2013Austrian Museum of Applied Arts/Contemporary Art]], and Marcello Farabegoli, curator and producer of the exhibition.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ambvienna.esteri.it/ambasciata_vienna/de/ambasciata/news/dall-ambasciata/2016/03/mostra-di-esther-stocker-in-ambasciata.html|title=Ausstellung von Esther Stocker in der Italienischen Botschaft|website=www.ambvienna.esteri.it|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marcello-farabegoli.net/geometrien.html|title=Geometrien|website=www.marcello-farabegoli.net|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.artribune.com/report/2016/04/mostra-esther-stocker-palazzo-metternich-vienna/|title=Geometrie d\u2019artista. Esther Stocker a Vienna - Artribune|first=Franco|last=Veremondi|date=11 April 2016|publisher=|acc